aVPresident Donald Trump on Tuesday morning touted progress in uniting the world against North Korea.\u000a\u000a"After many years of failure,countries are coming together to finally address the dangers posed by North Korea," he wrote on Twitter.\u000a\u000aAfter many years of failure,countries are coming together to finally address the dangers posed by North Korea. We must be tough & decisive! \u2014 Donald J. Trump (@realDonaldTrump) August 8, 2017\u000a\u000aHis post followed up on his reteweet of a "Fox & Friends" item about North Korea.newsf
